<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA621_02_IH_0006</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema621_02.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_02_ih_0006">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">
					실 
					<div class="fraction_box">
						<span>4</span>
						<span>21</span>
					</div>
					m로 독도 기념 팔찌를 한 개 만들 수 있습니다. 실 
					<div class="fraction_box">
						<span>16</span>
						<span>21</span>
					</div>
					m로 독도 기념 팔찌를 몇 개 만들 수 있는지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="flex justify_center">
					<img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA621_02_IH/0006_img.png" alt="">
				</div>
				<div class="question_box justify_center gap_120">
					<div class="flex align_center gap_4">
						<div class="flex gap_10">
							<span class="label_gray" lang="y">식</span>
							<div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap answer1">
								<math-field data-answer-single="(16)/(21)-:(4)/(21)"></math-field>
							</div>
						</div>
						=
						<div class="input_wrap">
							<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="flex gap_10">
						<span class="label_gray" lang="y">답</span>
						<div class="flex align_center gap_4">
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
							</div>
							<span lang="y">개</span>
						</div>
					</div>
						
				</div>
				
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve ml_20">
								<p class="mt_5">(만들 수 있는 독도 기념 팔찌 수)</p>
								<p class="in_flex mt_5">
								  =
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>16</span><span>21</span></span>
								  ÷
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>21</span></span>
								  = 16 ÷ 4 = 4(개)
								</p>
							  </div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve">
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
